15:13.080 --> 15:15.002
Y'all leave this alone
for now.

15:15.040 --> 15:17.179
Nova:
Wait, did you listen
to the whole interview?

15:17.210 --> 15:20.043
- Did she?
- Here, put this
on the table, please.

15:20.080 --> 15:22.139
Andre and Reggie
were just playing around.

15:22.180 --> 15:23.442
They say a bunch
of stupid stuff.

15:23.490 --> 15:25.139
