my words around now.

15:52.750 --> 15:56.049
What I said was
that's how rape victims
who come forward are portrayed.

15:56.080 --> 15:59.186
What you said sounded
like my sister calling
my husband a rapist.

15:59.220 --> 16:01.586
- Could maybe y'all
talk about this later?
- Come on, girls.

16:01.620 --> 16:04.180
So, suddenly
you believe in Davis now?

16:04.230 --> 16:06.255
He hasn't been truthful
about a single thing so far.

16:06.290 --> 16:08.599
If that whore,
Milena Galoudian,

16:08.630 --> 16:10.495
is such a victim,
then why is she asking

16:10.530 --> 16:14.990
