21:29.020 --> 21:31.443
I guess I was wrong.

21:31.490 --> 21:32.912
Actually...

21:32.950 --> 21:35.657
I do have all those people.

21:35.690 --> 21:37.954
You just couldn't fit them
on the private jet?

21:37.990 --> 21:40.049
- Saving costs.
- Got it.

21:40.090 --> 21:42.627
( laughing )

21:45.630 --> 21:46.699
( sighs )

21:46.730 --> 21:48.664
Charley's ridiculous.

21:48.700 --> 21:50.531
She's getting worked up
about a couple
of shock jocks--

21:50.570 --> 21:52.936
Cut Charley some slack.

21:54.980 --> 21:57.801
blown up on T.V.
like that.

21:57.850 --> 21:58.999
For real.

22:02.980 --> 22:06.541
How's the warehouse job
going?

22:06.590 --> 22:09.457
It's a job on top of the job
I already have.

22:09.490 --> 22:11.685
It is what it is.

22:11.730 --> 22:13.550
How much you got left
on your parole?

22:13.600 --> 22:15.693
A little over a year.

22:15.730 --> 22:17.960
Your parole officer okay?

22:18.000 --> 22:19.763
He all right.

22:19.800 --> 22:22.337
For a guy who make me pee
in a cup once a week.

22:23.740 --> 22:27.608
Checking on this,
checking on that.

22:27.640 --> 22:31.474
You know I got to take
a parenting class to learn
how to parent Blue?

22:32.880 --> 22:34.848
All they got to do
is see me with him

22:34.880 --> 22:37.986
to know
I know what I'm doing.

22:38.020 --> 22:40.818
You're doing all right,
Ralph.

22:43.530 --> 22:45.589
I was thinking,

22:45.630 --> 22:48.599
maybe I could ask Charley
to fill out my paperwork.

22:48.630 --> 22:50.598
So I could do this
for parole.

22:50.630 --> 22:53.599
What you need
to ask Charley for?
I'll sign it for you.

22:53.640 --> 22:56.666
I got to get paid,
40 hours, her money.

22:56.700 --> 22:58.463
Well, when we sell,
you can pay her back
out of that.

22:58.510 --> 23:00.808
Will you stop talking
about selling, Nova?

23:02.640 --> 23:07.646
* Humble I fall

23:08.720 --> 23:12.417
* Humble I fall *

23:12.450 --> 23:14.953
* To my knees

23:14.990 --> 23:19.859
* Humble I fall.

