23:24.470 --> 23:26.563
_ - Yeah.
- ( Violet screams )

23:26.600 --> 23:28.830
I am so glad you are back!

23:28.870 --> 23:30.633
What's up?

23:30.670 --> 23:32.069
Oh, baby,
we missed you.

23:32.110 --> 23:33.930
I missed you, too.

23:33.980 --> 23:36.505
Okay,
so I just picked up
some barbeque

23:36.540 --> 23:38.508
from the place
down the road.

23:38.550 --> 23:39.972
- Go on in there
and help yourself.
- Okay.

23:40.010 --> 23:42.513
The others will be in
from the field any minute.

23:42.550 --> 23:44.643
Hey, Vi, can you tell
Charley we're here, please?

23:44.690 --> 23:47.454
I said they're coming in
from the fields any minute.

23:47.490 --> 23:48.718
Charley?

23:48.760 --> 23:50.523
Yeah, isn't that her now?

23:50.560 --> 23:53.927
( laughing, talking )

23:53.960 --> 23:55.518
( Charley gasps )

23:55.560 --> 23:56.993
Hey!

23:57.030 --> 23:58.793
Wait, Mom.
Stop, stop, stop.
You're dirty.

23:58.830 --> 24:00.468
- You're dirty!
- Come on.

24:00.500 --> 24:01.933
A little dirt's good.
