24:03.970 --> 24:05.904
- What you say, Micah?
Welcome back, baby.
- What's up?

24:07.780 --> 24:09.600
Mr. Newell.

24:09.640 --> 24:11.972
- Remy, Micah.
- Remy.

24:14.650 --> 24:16.538
Micah,
better come on in here

24:16.580 --> 24:17.581
and get some
of these hot links

24:17.620 --> 24:18.746
before they're all gone.

24:18.790 --> 24:19.779
Go on.

24:20.890 --> 24:24.553
Oh, Davis,
this is Remy Newell.

24:24.590 --> 24:26.820
Remy, this is Davis.

24:26.860 --> 24:29.658
- Nice to meet you.
- Yeah, you too.

24:34.300 --> 24:36.564
If y'all don't mind,
I'm gonna go in here

24:36.600 --> 24:38.704
and grab some
of these hot links
before they're gone.

24:38.740 --> 24:40.628
Yup.

24:40.680 --> 24:41.772
( chuckles )

24:44.610 --> 24:45.975
So, is he a local farmer?

24:46.010 --> 24:47.511
No.

24:47.550 --> 24:49.518
No, he is an engineer.

24:49.550 --> 24:52.587
And a professor.

24:52.620 --> 24:54.258
Well, I...

24:54.290 --> 24:55.917
didn't think
you would get this, um,

24:55.960 --> 24:58.520
into farming.

24:58.560 --> 25:00.551
I've never seen you
water a houseplant.

25:03.830 --> 25:06.719
Let's get some lunch,
Davis.

25:06.770 --> 25:08.761
(faint talking )

25:15.780 --> 25:17.645
Davis.

25:17.680 --> 25:20.240
I'll wash up
and you can leave.

25:23.050 --> 25:25.018
Ralph Angel:
I'll see you out there,
Mr. Prosper.

25:25.050 --> 25:27.757
Prosper:
You're doing good, son,
you're doing good.

25:27.790 --> 25:30.679
Hey, uh.

25:30.730 --> 25:32.618
Micah showed me
your article.

25:32.660 --> 25:36.949
Yeah. It's good.
I can really relate,
you know?

25:37.000 --> 25:39.628
I've seen how the system
treats black men.

25:39.670 --> 25:43.333
Especially after living
through this witch hunt,
you know what I'm saying?

25:43.370 --> 25:46.533
When you're a black man
accused of something,
you must have done it.

25:50.340 --> 25:52.979
How'd you and Micah
get here, Davis?

25:53.010 --> 25:55.717
- We flew.
- Which airline?

25:55.750 --> 25:59.345
- Private.
-Hmm.

25:59.390 --> 26:01.711
