26:03.630 --> 26:05.586
So many paparazzi on me.

26:05.630 --> 26:07.325
Yeah.

26:07.360 --> 26:08.952
That's what I thought.

26:09.000 --> 26:11.662
Yeah.

26:11.700 --> 26:13.793
So, you flew private.

26:13.840 --> 26:14.989
You have a driver

26:15.040 --> 26:17.338
