back to Houston.

26:17.370 --> 26:22.376
Probably staying
in some fancy hotel
in the city.

26:22.410 --> 26:24.605
And you're paying millions
of dollars to pay off
your accuser

26:24.650 --> 26:26.641
so that you don't
have to stand trial.

26:29.280 --> 26:31.942
