comparing yourself
to a 17-year-old kid

26:31.990 --> 26:34.015
without so much
as a public defender

26:34.060 --> 26:35.857
because you're both black.

26:39.730 --> 26:41.254
Listen,

26:41.300 --> 26:44.690
I don't know what lies
you have to tell yourself,

26:44.730 --> 26:46.664
to get up each morning,

26:48.740 --> 26:51.334
but let me point out
the most obvious one.

26:53.070 --> 26:56.233
