to search your property.

31:07.030 --> 31:09.089
T & K Warehouse,
where you're employed,

31:09.130 --> 31:11.394
has asked to have all
they're employer re5idences
searched

31:11.430 --> 31:13.421
for stolen merchandise.

31:26.610 --> 31:30.239
- What's going on, Pops?
- They're just looking around.

31:30.280 --> 31:33.443
When Aunt Vi answers,
tell her to come out here
right away, okay?

31:33.490 --> 31:35.515
- Okay. Yes.
