31:38.560 --> 31:39.584
Go on.

31:42.630 --> 31:44.461
( clears throat )

32:11.260 --> 32:13.524
Got a key to the shed?

32:20.070 --> 32:22.061
Let's go.

32:40.750 --> 32:43.014
Go on.

32:45.430 --> 32:47.386
Open it.

32:53.100 --> 32:54.431
Step back.

32:55.700 --> 32:58.009
Step. Back.

33:34.840 --> 33:36.569
Okay.

33:37.840 --> 33:40.070
It's clear.

33:41.550 --> 33:44.383
Sorry to have bothered you.

33:44.420 --> 33:46.479
Have a good night.

34:15.180 --> 34:17.444
Aunt Vi.

